      <title>马来西亚不能排除数百万捐款流入哈马斯的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/malaysia-can-t-rule-out-if-millions-in-donations-went-to-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，马来西亚政府不能排除当地一家慈善机构是否向哈马斯输送了数百万美元，目前正在调查该组织涉嫌支持东南亚国家的保守派伊斯兰组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/malaysia-can-t-rule-out-if-millions-in-donations-went-to-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 08:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
